{"tid":825942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"山竹襲港後應停工？高志森：有早知冇乞兒","createTime":"2018-09-18T01:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T03:23:58.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":83,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"0c2f2c9cab0b86e3e0f64d8a54e59e5a92c54535","tid":825942,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T01:45:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180917/photo/bkn-20180917153900972-0917_00862_001_01p.jpg?20180917171238\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180917%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180917153900972-0917_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20180917171238&h=87bf7817&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n導演高志森出席活動時，提到昨日颱風「山竹」襲港，今日巿面混亂，是否應該停工？他笑言：「有早知冇乞兒，估唔到冧樹會影響到交通咁嚴重。我今朝七點幾出門口，由順利邨去彩虹地鐵站，沿途見到好多人行落山去地鐵站返工，未見過咁多人，沿途好多樹都冧咗，三條行車線得番一條，揸車都要5分鐘，我估行要半個鐘。啲樹冧晒，唔放得啲巴士出嚟，放咗巴士仲癱瘓，個個湧晒去地鐵站，地鐵都負荷唔到，今次係經驗同教訓，非戰之罪，因為咁強嘅颱風唔係時時有，當然都唔想有，呢個風仲勁過溫黛，但好慶幸冇乜傷亡，香港人真係有福氣。」 <br />\n<br />\n喺屋企暈船浪 <br />\n<br />\n他直言昨日首次在家中暈船浪：「我全日好乖留喺屋企睇電視同做嘢，但一起身就發覺成間屋都搖晃，我住30樓，真係未試過，搖咗兩個鐘，我最後要爬上床瞓喺度。」他表示整日除了風聲，只聽到救護車的聲音，覺得香港的公職人員很值得敬佩：「覺得個心好唔安樂，佢哋都有屋企人，所以真係好值得敬佩。」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180917/bkn-20180917153900972-0917_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180917%2Fbkn-20180917153900972-0917_00862_001.html&d=57EJI2h5IKG69o9%2FHbVeI49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=2c0bad2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180917/bkn-20180917153900972-0917_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"56ba5ac770a961ab5af8fba13fbf717e18497619","tid":825942,"uid":9683,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T01:46:25.000Z","msg":"冇乜傷亡"},{"pid":"21190d48fb20ffc0fe6e3490816e5e8467420fa7","tid":825942,"uid":10757,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T01:49:08.000Z","msg":"... 打完風覺得條街會乾淨，冇野阻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  高智商喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67ff7502b6d1979ea1cdc379118d67f21f3871df","tid":825942,"uid":207574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T01:55:00.000Z","msg":"政府啲決策人士下下都要出左事先知衰<br />\n你做嚟把 lun 咩 一堆庸人"},{"pid":"c421b2cc4982286c80d4ffdac258156d6ab1df91","tid":825942,"uid":69213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T01:58:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"efa23f243bd392eef622aca17ca2aaa3bb757f32","tid":825942,"uid":62815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:00:50.000Z","msg":"一啲遠見都無<br />\n靠你地香港含得撚啦"},{"pid":"7acd6705095fd288b28d55b955ac32717466e000","tid":825942,"uid":204306,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:01:00.000Z","msg":"低智商都係公屋撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ebe759aef5613cb697e964479fad7586e64d4d0","tid":825942,"uid":37413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:03:51.000Z","msg":"乜需要估嘅咩，香港第一日打大風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22876f16a5ae9f5ae2fc4385aa2abf94983afd88","tid":825942,"uid":63154,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:06:48.000Z","msg":"個個都用得呢句辯護，唯獨政府唔得，政府嘅最大功能就係應付災前災後問題"},{"pid":"33ba9a803165ed018ec4943ba89d2cfee572057d","tid":825942,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c421b2cc4982286c80d4ffdac258156d6ab1df91","tid":825942,"uid":69213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T01:58:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:16:46.000Z","msg":"住30樓，印象中四順冇30層高，應該係紀律部隊宿舍"},{"pid":"dabab9d185717add2a58da4d6d3d681e5143ce4e","tid":825942,"uid":56321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"rep